from her son's inspiration,

20:15.839 --> 20:18.884
would want more than anything to show up

20:18.967 --> 20:22.304
at his memorial service
to pay your respects.

20:22.387 --> 20:24.389
Okay. [laughing]

20:24.473 --> 20:28.018
Is this a joke?
Did Ralphie put you up to this?

20:28.101 --> 20:33.273
