that the world's most wanted fugitive
is arranging his memorial service?

36:20.678 --> 36:24.807
People often hide from me.
Glen was good at finding them.

36:24.891 --> 36:29.353
I didn't ask you what he did.
I asked what made him special.

36:29.437 --> 36:31.522
That's a bit more complicated.

36:31.606 --> 36:33.065
I'm sure it is.

36:33.149 --> 36:37.570
I'm sure it's incredibly complicated,
and weird and strange.

36:38.070 --> 36:41.782
-But... I like weird and strange.
-Ah.

36:41.866 --> 36:44.994
You said I could ask for any favor.
That's the favor.

36:45.077 --> 36:49.290
You want me to tell you about
how weird and strange Glen was?

36:49.373 --> 36:53.502
I want to hear your eulogy.
I want Raymond Reddington to tell me

36:53.586 --> 36:57.340
what was weird, and strange, and beautiful

36:57.423 --> 37:00.676
about the regional manager
of the Rockville DMV.

37:01.552 --> 37:04.722
You know who I am.
I can do some very big favors.

37:04.805 --> 37:05.765
[chuckles]

37:05.848 --> 37:08.017
Trust me, I thought about asking you

37:08.100 --> 37:10.353
to scare the bejesus
out of my pal Bruce Hornsby.

37:11.229 --> 37:14.398
That'd have been good. But the truth is,

37:14.482 --> 37:18.736
you can't do a bigger favor
than revealing somebody's heart and soul.

37:18.819 --> 37:20.238
No. I don't suppose you can.

37:20.321 --> 37:23.574
Yeah. I did my part. I gave my eulogy.

37:23.658 --> 37:26.953
And in exchange,
I'd like to hear your version.

37:29.664 --> 37:32.083
Mr. Lewis. Big fan.

37:32.166 --> 37:33.084
Thanks.

37:38.256 --> 37:39.882
What? What is that?

37:39.966 --> 37:43.135
The remains of a Great Dane.
We're friends with a vet.

37:43.219 --> 37:46.347
He works at a shelter where they cremate
pets who have to be put down.

37:46.430 --> 37:48.266
But I told you I won't steal his ashes.

37:48.349 --> 37:51.686
And I know you well enough to know
that in the end you probably would.

37:52.270 --> 37:57.024
I'm sorry, but what's going on with all
the beans, and the baggies and the ashes?

37:57.108 --> 37:59.402
I'll explain everything on the way.

38:03.072 --> 38:05.199
<i>âª Let's have a good time âª</i>

38:24.093 --> 38:26.137
Okay. [chuckles]

38:26.679 --> 38:27.763
Here we are.

38:28.514 --> 38:30.266
-Glen.
-Right.

38:31.726 --> 38:32.560
Glen.

38:38.065 --> 38:39.358
Glen was...

38:42.778 --> 38:44.613
so many different things.

38:46.324 --> 38:47.283
A son.

38:48.701 --> 38:50.119
A civil servant.

38:51.996 --> 38:55.458
Proud member of the Spare Me bowling team.

38:55.541 --> 39:01.547
Two-time runner-up
at the Southern Regional Tournament.

39:02.173 --> 39:06.469
And a great, a truly great tracker.

39:07.970 --> 39:09.513
But he was--

39:10.723 --> 39:12.058
Oh, brother.

39:14.602 --> 39:16.771
He was a lot more than that.

39:19.231 --> 39:20.483
Glen was...

39:21.776 --> 39:23.402
infuriating.

39:24.362 --> 39:25.654
Insulting.

39:26.697 --> 39:29.325
Just so maddening.

39:30.368 --> 39:35.164
He was a hedonist, chauvinist,
a liar, a cheat,

39:35.247 --> 39:39.960
but there was one thing... Glen was not.

39:45.257 --> 39:46.634
And that's afraid.

39:47.259 --> 39:51.180
Glen was... not afraid.

39:51.764 --> 39:55.393
He wasn't afraid of judgment,
of being wrong.

39:55.476 --> 39:58.896
He wasn't afraid of friendship or romance.

39:58.979 --> 40:02.066
A bad joke. A good laugh.

40:03.192 --> 40:07.613
He was never afraid
of a good time, or bad timing...

40:08.197 --> 40:09.782
or consequences...

40:10.449 --> 40:12.952
or of an impossible task...

40:14.412 --> 40:17.665
or any kind of danger.

40:19.375 --> 40:23.003
And he certainly
wasn't afraid of me, ever.

40:24.713 --> 40:26.173
[emotional music playing]

40:26.257 --> 40:32.388
No matter how hard
or unfair life was to Glen...

40:33.180 --> 40:35.808
Glen loved life back.

40:36.976 --> 40:42.690
He embraced it without reservation,
regret, or remorse.

40:44.024 --> 40:45.985
And that is...

40:49.572 --> 40:50.489
rare.

41:00.499 --> 41:01.417
I wish--

41:04.962 --> 41:09.216
I wish more people
were unafraid like Glen.

41:12.928 --> 41:16.557
It's the thing about him
I'll miss the most.

41:24.440 --> 41:29.487
And I hope it'll be some time before...

41:33.908 --> 41:36.118
all my memories of him...

41:40.539 --> 41:41.957
start to fade.

42:50.985 --> 42:52.987
[theme music playing]
